io.fdeitylink.keroedit.util

Interface SafeEnum<E extends java.lang.Enum<E>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    KeroEdit.ActionsMenuItem, KeroEdit.EditMenuItem, KeroEdit.FileMenuItem, KeroEdit.HelpMenuItem, KeroEdit.MapListMenuItem, KeroEdit.ViewMenuItem, MapEditTab.DrawMode, MapEditTab.LayerFlag, MapEditTab.MapPaneMenuItem, MapEditTab.ViewFlag

    public interface SafeEnum<E extends java.lang.Enum<E>>
    Marker interface for Enums whose ordinals can be relied on to be unchanged. Useful for enums that are used for array or list indexes.
